Ticket 2 — Browser Not Loading Pages
User: Kevin R.
Department: Customer Support
Issue: “Chrome keeps spinning. Edge works fine.”

🔍 Technician Notes
Issue isolated to Chrome

Likely cache, profile corruption, or extension issue

🧪 Troubleshooting Steps
Ran Browser Diagnostics Script

Verified DNS Resolution

Checked Browser Cache Size

Disabled all Chrome extensions

Tested in Incognito mode

✅ Resolution
Chrome profile was corrupted. Renamed:

Code
%LOCALAPPDATA%\Google\Chrome\User Data\Default → Default.old
Chrome recreated a clean profile and browsing returned to normal.

📌 Preventative Recommendation
Encourage user to limit unnecessary extensions.
